FRIDAY, i finally get to share the first taste of my ROCK MUSIC with the world 😭 PLEASE PRE-SAVE my cover of “You Oughta Know” now!! link in bio OF COURSE!
-
if you’ve been around for a while you know that alanis morissette is one of my favorite artists, and this song has been me go-to karaoke for LIFE, so the fact that i was able to reimagine it in my own voice and style is so fucking magical to me. THIS is the artist i was always meant to be 🥲 get ready to rock the fuck out!
